&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Prior to
commencement of development hereby approved, a tree protection plan and method
statement in accordance with BS5837:2012 shall be submitted for approval by the
Local Planning Authority. Issues to be dealt with in the TPP and AMS:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Specification for protective fencing and
     a plan indicating the alignment of the fencing. Tree protection during
     construction clearly indicated on a TPP and construction exclusion zones
     clearly shown&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Methods of demolition within the RPA of
     retained trees&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Details of construction within the RPA
     including any no-dig driveways and parking areas to be constructed using a
     no-dig specification. Details should include levels and cross-sections&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Details of arboricultural site
     supervision and monitoring. Details of reporting of inspection and
     supervision&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Details of site access, storage of
     materials, fuel, concrete mixing, use of fires, parking, welfare etc&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Details of any facilitation pruning&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;The
development thereafter will be implemented in strict accordance with the
approved details.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;





&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
